QuestData.Title: Supply Recovery
QuestData.Description: We seem to have arrived at just the right time!$b$bThe Gordunni have been enchanting armaments for the Iron Horde and it looks like they haven't picked up the latest shipment.$b$bWe could put that gear to far better use! Lets go hunt down their shipping containers. I brought some signal flares that we can use to call in an air pick-up when we've secured the shipment.
QuestData.RewardText: Alright, that should be the last one we need. $b$bNothing feels as good as knowing you are stronger than your enemy!
